casebody.data:
Monday, December 27, 1999

MOTION DOCKET

99-1452. State v. Braden.

Franklin C.P. No. 98CR084601. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Common Pleas of Franklin County. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of execution set for June 16, 2000, pending disposition of his appeal by this court,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay be, and hereby is, granted.
